Instructions for setting up your own hotkeys

    Open the menu by pressing they key that is on the left of your right "Ctrl" key (it's below the enter key).
    Picture of where the key is: https://www.pic2web.net/upload/779e3b77c5fe6e0bad9a6d9036ab9f6bf146c479.png
    
    Change following keybindings in the following tabs:
    1. Config-tab | Menu key
    2. Visuals-tab | Toggle key
    3. Triggerbot-tab | Triggerkey for every weapon(-category) that is marked as active

For new members I offer to create a config fitting to their likes. Contact me on the forums and I will answer shortly.
